snippet.title: Fallout 76 - Official ‘Road to Atlantic City’ Trailer | Xbox Games Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Fallout 76 is not only celebrating over 15 million players but also unveiling content for the game. Players will be able to explore an all-new location beyond Appalachia, Atlantic City. Vault-Dwellers will be able to explore locations from before the war and new enemies to defeat. New clothing, weapons, and more will be available for players to acquire. Fallout 76’s Atlantic City is coming soon.

#IGN #Xbox #SoG
